[2] Blast disease - Jammu and Kashmir
Date: Thu 13 Sep 2018
Source: Greater Kashmir [edited]
https://www.greaterkashmir.com/news/business/rice-blast-disease-affects-paddy-in-karnah-areas/296261.html


Farmers in Kupwara [district] expressed their resentment over outbreak of rice blast disease in their area. A delegation said 75 per cent of their paddy crop has been damaged by the disease. They accused [the] Agriculture Department. "The department failed to provide necessary chemical sprays to overcome rice blast," they said.

[Byline: Peerzada Sayeed]

